  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TPa12">
<l>kaṉaittiḷam kaṟṟerumai kaṉṟukkiraṅki</l>
<l>niṉaittu mulai vaḻiyē niṉṟu pāl cōra</l>
<l>naṉaittillam cēṟākkum naṟ celvaṉ taṅkāy</l>
<l>paṉit talai vīḻa niṉ vācaṟ kaṭai paṟṟic</l>
<l>ciṉattiṉāl teṉ ilaṅkaik kōmāṉaic ceṟṟa</l>
<l>maṉattukkiṉiyāṉaip pāṭavum nī vāy tiṟavāy</l>
<l>iṉittāṉ eḻuntirāy īteṉṉa pēr uṟakkam</l>
<l>aṉaittillattārum aṟintēlōr empāvāy</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O sister of the good, wealthy man,</l>
<l rend="indent">whose house the buffaloes with young calves drench [and] turn into slush,</l>
<l rend="indent">having bellowed, thought of [and] been distressed for the calves,</l>
<l rend="indent">as milk exudes through the[ir] udders!</l>
<l>You will not open [your] mouth</l>
<l>[even] as we,</l>
<l rend="indent">holding the entrance gate as dew falls on [our] heads,</l>
<l rend="indent">sing [about]</l>
<l rend="indent">Him who is sweet to the manas,</l>
<l rend="indent">who destroyed the king of Laṅkā in the South out of anger!</l>
<l>Get up at least now! What is this great slumber?</l>
<l>The people from all the houses [here] have learnt [about it]!</l>
<l>O our maidens, accept [and] consider [this] attentively!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
